{"tid":2137131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"咩叫臨床檢驗技術人員？香港叫醫務化驗師。","createTime":"2020-08-02T16:07:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T17:33:22.000Z","uid":81046,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"09c19d7854071c78e5e7080854ce56c700bf552a","tid":2137131,"uid":81046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T16:07:39.000Z","msg":"所謂檢測人員，香港叫醫務化驗師，專職醫療既一種，要拎牌，要註冊，受規管 （Cap 359a)。<br />\n<br />\n香港所有醫學/臨床化驗，包括核酸檢測都要由持有效執業證明書既註冊醫務化驗師處理。<br />\n<br />\n利申：守法意識強烈，班臨床檢驗技術人員唔好犯法呀，實捉到你。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"157ff8c9e20c44e96c147f05d13ee236730734b0","tid":2137131,"uid":81046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T16:08:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b76150047a05fc13e5caf9c50f80b994c20d0a61","tid":2137131,"uid":81046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T16:09:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a79b3f7e2ccff0ec6c1980ab41ca62f5308c516","tid":2137131,"uid":81046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T16:10:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62ffe884ba5ac277e03ea6c69ebb7b24c3e16dfd","tid":2137131,"uid":81046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T16:11:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6bbbe25628c021af6d2ac12f25df5791696b801","tid":2137131,"uid":81046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T16:12:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3115a38a50d1b7e8d057055fed4aa6466b5e413d","tid":2137131,"uid":81046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T16:13:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7243ff6482d70f8a345a0e8bbfc1052db